  <brief_title>Cotton Sock in Pediatric Patients With Leg-foot Splint</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effectiveness of Cotton Sock in Pediatric Patients With Leg-foot Splint After Surgery for Correction of the Foot, in Reducing the Incidence of Cutaneous Lesions. Randomized Controlled Trial.</official_title>
